# Tauri Cargo.toml

Never remove `macos-private-api` from the `tauri` features in `src-tauri/Cargo.toml`.

This project uses transparent overlay windows (quick todo, eye-care reminder) via `auxiliary_windows.rs`. The feature is required on macOS even though it is harmless on other platforms.

```toml
# ✅ KEEP — required for macOS transparent overlays
tauri = { version = "2", features = ["protocol-asset", "tray-icon", "macos-private-api"] }

# ❌ NEVER do this during refactors or cross-platform fixes
tauri = { version = "2", features = ["protocol-asset", "tray-icon"] }
```

Do not "simplify" or "normalize" this line when editing unrelated code.
